{"TopicId":187499,"ForumId":109,"TopicTitle":"Double runways?!","CreatedByName":"GoldForest","CreatedById":77770,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T06:34:00Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"GoldForest","CreatedById":77770,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T06:34:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just watched the\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=126\u0026amp;v=5uqpdoFCOMM\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Einterview\u003C/a\u003E and saw that the new \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E not only has several different sizes of launch pads, with mobile launch towers mind you (Probably just aesthetic, no real functionality, but there are tracks on those towers), but it also has TWO runways. Yes TWO!\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nMy question now is... will the hanger allow us to build craft large enough to need both runways, or is it just aesthetic. If it\u0027s just aesthetic, then could someone please at launch port the hanger extender mod to KSP2 so we can make double runway wide planes!\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerikBalm","CreatedById":91917,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T07:48:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know of no plane that uses two runways, in fact I think that\u0027s a stupid idea. Instead I think that two runways would be interesting from a multiplayer perspective, simultaneous launches of 2 planes!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-08-22T07:49:37Z\u0022 title=\u002208/22/2019 07:49  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 22, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by KerikBalm\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GoldForest","CreatedById":77770,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T07:51:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223656495\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187499\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566460097\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002291917\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KerikBalm\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, KerikBalm said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know of no plane that uses two runways, in fact I think that\u0027s a stupid idea. Instead I think that two runways would be interesting from a multiplayer perspective, simultaneous launches of 2 planes!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat time point did you see the two runways?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDuring the launch of the first wobbly rocket. Also, a plane launch Saturn V would have to be HUGE!!! Double runway huge.\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nWait for the rocket to start rolling and flipping over and pause it as soon as you see the runways. Also, are those helipads near the runway?!\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/5uqpdoFCOMM?start=280\u0026amp;feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-08-22T07:51:30Z\u0022 title=\u002208/22/2019 07:51  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 22, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by GoldForest\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T13:39:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe design will definitely be taking multiplayer into account, so that would be my guess as well.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GoldForest","CreatedById":77770,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T13:45:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223656692\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187499\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566481193\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184845\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MechBFP\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, MechBFP said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe design will definitely be taking multiplayer into account, so that would be my guess as well.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTrue, but one giant plane able to launch a Saturn V is a nice prospect as well.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerikBalm","CreatedById":91917,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T15:02:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can do that in KSP already, or close to it:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022NOkk5JA.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/NOkk5JA.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00228YcJY6h.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/8YcJY6h.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have better screenshots at home, but I haven\u0027t uploaded them on imgur\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GoldForest","CreatedById":77770,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T15:23:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223656755\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187499\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566486160\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002291917\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KerikBalm\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 minutes ago, KerikBalm said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can do that in KSP already, or close to it:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/NOkk5JA.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022NOkk5JA.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/NOkk5JA.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/8YcJY6h.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u00228YcJY6h.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/8YcJY6h.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have better screenshots at home, but I haven\u0027t uploaded them on imgur\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot a Saturn V, but I know. But I still want a MASSIVE plane. Double runway wide massive. I like my planes big.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ThatGuyWithALongUsername","CreatedById":140817,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T15:56:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt also had about 4 vertical landing pads as well, right next to the runway.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GoldForest","CreatedById":77770,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T15:57:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223656800\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187499\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566489369\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022140817\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ThatGuyWithALongUsername\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, ThatGuyWithALongUsername said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt also had about 4 vertical landing pads as well, right next to the runway.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have another thread where I speculate there\u0027s actually 5\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidCosmos","CreatedById":192336,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T17:10:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223656495\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187499\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566460097\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002291917\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KerikBalm\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, KerikBalm said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know of no plane that uses two runways, in fact I think that\u0027s a stupid idea. Instead I think that two runways would be interesting from a multiplayer perspective, simultaneous launches of 2 planes!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDanny will show you!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003E(Some day......)\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ThatGuyWithALongUsername","CreatedById":140817,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T18:11:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust make a reeeeeeeally wide double-fuselaged plane (stratolaunch style) and use both runways at once!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}